============================================================================
Author: Pavlo Boidachenko                                   Date: 10.08.2018
============================================================================
                                
                            Description.

Fine way to close auto complete menu after exiting insert mode using 'jj' 
shortcut, when using Vintage mode with Sublime Text 3.

                            Instruction.

1. Put macros file exit_insert_mode.sublime-macro into .../Packages/User/
   directory.
2. Open your Sublime Key Buildings preferences and put there text from
   'Default (OSX).sublime-keymap' file.
3. For your comfort i suggest to reduce auto_complete_delay value in 
   Preferences, because sometimes autocomplete menu shows up after
   you type 'jj' and not closes. 
4. Done.

